00:30:24.456 --> 00:30:26.858 align:middle line:84%
Well, take our leaders, put
them in a big arena, you know,

00:30:26.858 --> 00:30:29.494 align:middle line:84%
and we get to pay, you
know, 10 dollars to watch.

00:30:29.494 --> 00:30:30.896 align:middle line:90%
Now that would be entertainment.

00:30:30.896 --> 00:30:33.265 align:middle line:84%
>> Noory: John McAfee, thank you
